annotationA: Protein cycle; Putative transcription factor involved in the generation of biological rhythms. Activates cycling transcription of Period (PER) and Timeless (TIM) by binding to the E-box (5'-CACGTG-3') present in their promoters
annotationB: Supernumerary limbs, isoform B; Ubiquitin-protein transferase activity; phosphoprotein binding; protein dimerization activity
